### Get all directors (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/directors

### Get all directors (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/directors?_page=2&_limit=10

### Get director by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/directors/3

### Create director
POST http://localhost:5000/api/directors HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test director",
  "country": "United States of America",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01",
  "death_date": null,
  "photo": null,
  "biography": null
}

### Update director (full)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/directors HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": 29,
  "full_name": "Updated director",
  "country": "United States of America",
  "birth_date": "2000-01-01",
  "death_date": "2000-01-01",
  "photo": null,
  "biography": null
}

### Update director (patch)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/directors/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Patched director",
  "country": "Great Britain (England)"
}

### Delete director
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/directors/29 HTTP/1.1
